lines.text: It feels like my insides are on fire.
There's nothing wrong with people needing each other.
[Ariel attempts to communicate with the monster]
Stop! Stop right there! Don't hurt him! You're part of him! You're part of me!
You have come at last - the prophecy has been fulfilled.
A mutant sperm of some sort, forcing its way into the embryo, fusing with it, battling for genetic dominance!
